    title: 'NYC Visitor&apos;s Guide: How to Get from the Airport to Your Hotel',
    description: 'First time visiting New York City? This complete guide covers how to get from JFK, LaGuardia, and Newark airports to your Manhattan hotel — with honest advice on taxis, Uber, and black car service.',
    metaDescription: 'Complete guide for first-time NYC visitors arriving by air. How to get from JFK, LGA, and EWR to Manhattan hotels. Compare yellow cabs, Uber, subway, and professional car service.',
    keywords: ['NYC airport to hotel', 'JFK to Manhattan hotel', 'NYC visitor transportation', 'airport transfer NYC hotel', 'first time NYC airport transfer'],
    date: '2026-06-25',
